    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would be a solid choice for someone looking for a functional car at a more accessible price point. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some fading on the clear coat in certain areas. Inside, the upholstery has some visible wear and staining, and some of the plastic trim pieces show scuffing from regular use. Mechanically, the car starts and runs reliably, though it may require some routine maintenance and minor repairs in the near future to keep it in top shape. It's a dependable driver for someone who prioritizes utility over aesthetics.",
