    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a definitive example of the E46 M3, powered by the legendary S54B32 inline-six engine featuring individual throttle bodies and double VANOS. This vehicle is paired with a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a variable M differential lock for optimal torque distribution. The mechanical condition is superlative, with documented rod bearing replacement and proactive subframe reinforcement already completed. The suspension geometry remains tight, preserving the car's celebrated 50/50 weight distribution and analog steering feedback. A true collector-grade specimen with no deferred maintenance, delivering peak performance up to its 8,000 RPM redline.",
